00:31:45,119 --> 00:31:46,119
I'm fine too.

493
00:31:47,240 --> 00:31:49,680
I terminated the contract with Zhou Quan.

494
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:52,440
Is that so?

495
00:31:53,119 --> 00:31:54,480
You have to be careful.

496
00:31:54,799 --> 00:31:56,400
That's right.

497
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,240
I'm not your client anymore.

498
00:31:58,559 --> 00:32:00,200
You're not my bodyguard anymore.

499
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:02,319
Can't we see each other more often?

500
00:32:06,279 --> 00:32:08,880
Unfortunately, I just signed for a new job.

501
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:10,960
Who is it?

502
00:32:11,119 --> 00:32:12,160
Is it a man or a woman?

503
00:32:12,839 --> 00:32:13,880
A man.

504
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:16,559
He is a young boss.

505
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:20,359
Your company is full of staff.

506
00:32:20,359 --> 00:32:21,880
Why do you have to do it?

507
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:23,519
I think it's convenient.

508
00:32:23,759 --> 00:32:27,319
I look more like a secretary or an assistant.

509
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:28,599
It's low-key.

510
00:32:30,799 --> 00:32:31,799
By the way,

511
00:32:32,559 --> 00:32:33,839
in two days,

512
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:36,000
I'll have to go to a meeting abroad with him.

513
00:32:37,279 --> 00:32:38,319
A meeting?

514
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,000
No way.

515
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:42,240
Why not?

516
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,279
Look.

517
00:32:43,279 --> 00:32:45,680
You are going abroad with him alone.

518
00:32:45,680 --> 00:32:47,799
It's dangerous. There is no one to keep you safe.

519
00:32:47,799 --> 00:32:48,880
I'm worried.

520
00:32:49,559 --> 00:32:51,000
It's my job.

521
00:32:51,759 --> 00:32:54,000
I hate it when you say that.

522
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:55,720
You keep saying that it's your job.

523
00:32:56,079 --> 00:32:57,440
You're so charming when you're working.

524
00:32:57,440 --> 00:32:58,839
What if he likes you?

525
00:32:58,839 --> 00:32:59,839
I would be so worried.

526
00:33:01,319 --> 00:33:04,039
I can't skip my work just because you don't agree.

527
00:33:05,039 --> 00:33:06,400
Okay then. You can get back to work.

528
00:33:06,720 --> 00:33:08,880
Work hard to make money. Bye.

529
00:33:23,039 --> 00:33:24,039
Yes.

530
00:33:25,359 --> 00:33:26,720
By the way, there's one more thing.

531
00:33:27,559 --> 00:33:29,599
Sell my two villas.

532
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:34,559
Pay back the bank loan with the money.

533
00:33:34,559 --> 00:33:35,799
Use the rest of it...

534
00:33:36,160 --> 00:33:39,000
to settle the mortgage on Hou Jue's condominium.

535
00:33:39,359 --> 00:33:40,359
Okay.

536
00:33:41,519 --> 00:33:42,559
Yes.

537
00:33:43,039 --> 00:33:44,079
Please.

538
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:47,400
Mr. Hou.

539
00:33:48,240 --> 00:33:49,279
Why are you...

540
00:33:49,519 --> 00:33:51,200
Are you really going to sell the villas?

541
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:52,640
Yes.

542
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:56,519
They're such nice houses. It's a waste to sell them.

543
00:33:58,960 --> 00:34:01,079
It's okay. They're just material possessions.

544
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:04,599
Ms. Zhang.

545
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:09,719
When I was in the hospital bed...

546
00:34:10,329 --> 00:34:11,769
Do you know...

547
00:34:13,519 --> 00:34:15,920
When I thought I was going to die,

548
00:34:16,809 --> 00:34:20,809
I realized that nothing mattered at that moment.

549
00:34:20,809 --> 00:34:22,360
Be it the cars or the properties.

550
00:34:23,079 --> 00:34:24,239
They are pointless.

551
00:34:25,159 --> 00:34:26,809
They can't help me.

552
00:34:27,519 --> 00:34:30,840
But when I opened my eyes and saw Hou Jue looking at me,

553
00:34:34,079 --> 00:34:36,360
I felt secure.

554
00:34:37,599 --> 00:34:38,880
Yes, that's right.

555
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,519
You...

556
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:45,679
I could say that you were on the brink of death.

557
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:46,840
That's right.

558
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:48,559
Living alone in that big house...

559
00:34:49,329 --> 00:34:52,079
felt so empty.

560
00:34:53,329 --> 00:34:54,519
I woke up alone.

561
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,480
I ate alone.

562
00:34:57,769 --> 00:35:00,079
After a long day at work,

563
00:35:00,519 --> 00:35:02,329
I went back to my room and slept alone.

564
00:35:04,360 --> 00:35:05,960
It didn't feel like home.

565
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:07,119
Yes.

566
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:08,920
I...

567
00:35:09,719 --> 00:35:10,920
I have another idea.

568
00:35:12,119 --> 00:35:14,880
After I sell these two villas,

569
00:35:16,239 --> 00:35:18,079
I will continue staying here.

570
00:35:18,289 --> 00:35:20,039
If I overstay my welcome one day...

571
00:35:20,039 --> 00:35:24,599
and Hou Jue tells me to go back to my own house,

572
00:35:24,809 --> 00:35:26,289
I will tell him that I have sold my house.

573
00:35:26,289 --> 00:35:28,119
I will ask him where else he wants me to live.

574
00:35:28,119 --> 00:35:29,440
So I will live here.

575
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:32,239
He can't kick me out. I'm his dad.

576
00:35:32,239 --> 00:35:33,360
That's a good idea.

577
00:35:36,119 --> 00:35:37,719
All right. I'll get Hou Jue.

578
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,079
All right.

579
00:35:50,079 --> 00:35:52,719
Hou Jue, it's time to eat.

580
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:04,119
Hou Jue.

581
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,119
Hou Jue.

582
00:36:13,289 --> 00:36:15,840
Hou Jue, are you inside?

583
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:22,559
Where did he go?

584
00:36:29,679 --> 00:36:31,119
That Hou Jue...

585
00:36:31,239 --> 00:36:32,519
Didn't he just come back?

586
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:34,199
He's not in his room.

587
00:36:34,199 --> 00:36:36,239
He always does everything in a rush.

588
00:36:36,239 --> 00:36:37,329
Yes.

589
00:36:38,199 --> 00:36:40,809
Ms. Zhang, Hou Jue isn't home, right?

590
00:36:41,289 --> 00:36:42,559
Make me some braised meat.

591
00:36:42,559 --> 00:36:43,559
I can't do that.

592
00:36:43,559 --> 00:36:45,880
- It's fine to have it occasionally. - No, you can't have any meat.

593
00:36:46,329 --> 00:36:47,960
I'll take good care of you.

594
00:36:48,079 --> 00:36:50,519
Do you know what this is called? "A tiger getting its claws clipped."

595
00:36:51,239 --> 00:36:52,559
That brat.

596
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:55,159
I'm a nobody now in this family.

597
00:36:55,559 --> 00:36:57,289
You can't say that about him.

598
00:36:58,079 --> 00:36:59,199
I'm telling you.

599
00:36:59,559 --> 00:37:01,559
Your son wants what's best for you.

600
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:04,000
You don't know, right?

601
00:37:04,159 --> 00:37:07,000
He's very affectionate.

602
00:37:08,119 --> 00:37:09,920
When he wanted to be independent last time,

603
00:37:10,039 --> 00:37:11,480
he didn't take anything...

604
00:37:12,769 --> 00:37:15,199
except for the portrait.

605
00:37:26,769 --> 00:37:28,159
Back then,

606
00:37:29,119 --> 00:37:31,079
Yu Jie kept complaining that I was too busy with work...

607
00:37:32,119 --> 00:37:33,199
and I didn't keep her company.

608
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:36,440
I'm not that busy now.

609
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,880
She died too soon.

610
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:49,559
She didn't even get to see...

611
00:37:51,239 --> 00:37:52,599
every up and down that I went through.

612
00:37:54,769 --> 00:37:56,159
If only...

613
00:37:58,360 --> 00:38:00,519
she had stayed with me until now,

614
00:38:02,559 --> 00:38:05,440
she would have seen how glorious the company was...

615
00:38:06,329 --> 00:38:08,289
under my care.

616
00:38:08,559 --> 00:38:11,960
Your mind is only filled with glory.

617
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:15,400
Have you ever thought...

618
00:38:15,719 --> 00:38:16,840
how she got through...

619
00:38:17,719 --> 00:38:19,199
those few years?

620
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:23,360
How did she get through it?

621
00:38:26,239 --> 00:38:27,960
Ms. Zhang, don't you know?

622
00:38:27,960 --> 00:38:30,679
I was really busy with work.

623
00:38:31,199 --> 00:38:34,119
I gave her every penny I made at the company.

624
00:38:34,119 --> 00:38:35,920
She could have whatever she wanted.

625
00:38:36,639 --> 00:38:38,239
But when I got home, she would still fight with me.

626
00:38:38,239 --> 00:38:41,039
I didn't even know what I could do to make her satisfied.

627
00:38:41,960 --> 00:38:43,039
Hou Zhi Rong.

628
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:45,679
I've been working for you for almost 30 years.

629
00:38:45,809 --> 00:38:47,480
I've always called you Mr. Hou.

630
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:50,920
But today, I'll call you Zhi Rong.

631
00:38:52,119 --> 00:38:53,119
In the past few years,

632
00:38:53,119 --> 00:38:54,519
I've always wanted to tell you something.

633
00:38:55,039 --> 00:38:57,199
Hear me out, okay?

634
00:38:59,119 --> 00:39:01,000
Sure, go ahead.

635
00:39:04,119 --> 00:39:06,920
Yes, all these years,

636
00:39:07,199 --> 00:39:08,769
you've always been busy with work.

637
00:39:08,769 --> 00:39:10,039
You've worked so hard.

638
00:39:10,039 --> 00:39:11,519
I understand that.

639
00:39:12,329 --> 00:39:14,159
But do you know...

640
00:39:14,599 --> 00:39:16,840
how tiring and exhausting it is...

641
00:39:17,809 --> 00:39:20,440
for a woman to take care of a family on her own?

642
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:23,289
Hou Jue was very weak when he was young.

643
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:26,239
He had a fever almost every month and had to be hospitalized.

644
00:39:26,239 --> 00:39:28,920
But Yu Jie didn't want to disturb you,

645
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:31,289
so she never told you these things.

646
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:34,920
She was waiting for you to come home every day...

647
00:39:35,239 --> 00:39:38,719
so that you could keep her company, talk to her,

648
00:39:38,719 --> 00:39:40,039
and show your concern for her.

649
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:43,599
But did you ever spend time with her every time you came back?

650
00:39:44,840 --> 00:39:46,769
What do you call this?

651
00:39:47,559 --> 00:39:48,559
This...

652
00:39:49,039 --> 00:39:50,199
is cold violence.

653
00:39:51,199 --> 00:39:52,199
Back then,

654
00:39:52,329 --> 00:39:54,639
what she said the most was,

655
00:39:55,119 --> 00:39:58,159
"It's the same whether I have a husband or not."

656
00:39:58,719 --> 00:40:01,920
She cried in front of me several times.

657
00:40:02,599 --> 00:40:03,920
She kept telling me...

658
00:40:04,480 --> 00:40:06,599
that she suspected that you had another woman.

659
00:40:08,329 --> 00:40:10,440
You never took her seriously.

660
00:40:11,159 --> 00:40:12,480
You never...

661
00:40:13,079 --> 00:40:14,119
took this family seriously either.

662
00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:17,329
It's true that I had a lot going on at the time.

663
00:40:17,329 --> 00:40:18,809
When I got home, I felt sleepy.

664
00:40:18,809 --> 00:40:20,119
That was why I didn't talk to her.

665
00:40:20,119 --> 00:40:21,519
I would leave the house early the next morning.

666
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:23,360
I didn't have an affair.

667
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:25,119
I didn't have the time for that.

668
00:40:25,289 --> 00:40:27,519
I've never done anything to betray her.

669
00:40:28,079 --> 00:40:29,920
Yes, I know.

670
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:31,360
I told her that too.

671
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:33,289
But what you did...

672
00:40:34,239 --> 00:40:36,519
was indeed suspicious.

673
00:40:37,239 --> 00:40:38,329
And...

674
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:40,480
do you really know...

675
00:40:41,199 --> 00:40:42,480
your son?

676
00:40:43,360 --> 00:40:45,519
Do you know what he thinks about every day?

677
00:40:45,519 --> 00:40:46,599
Do you know what he does?

678
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:48,289
Ever since he started to understand things,

679
00:40:48,719 --> 00:40:49,880
what he saw...

680
00:40:50,159 --> 00:40:52,559
was just how tired...

681
00:40:53,239 --> 00:40:55,039
and how upset his mom was.

682
00:40:55,559 --> 00:40:56,559
So...

683
00:40:57,809 --> 00:40:59,199
he always believes...

684
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:02,559
it's your fault that his mom left.

685
00:41:06,809 --> 00:41:07,840
I'm sorry.

686
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:13,519
It's all my fault.

687
00:41:17,289 --> 00:41:18,769
Thank you, Ms. Zhang.

688
00:41:19,480 --> 00:41:21,840
Thank you for telling me this today.

689
00:41:24,360 --> 00:41:25,880
If you hadn't told me,

690
00:41:31,769 --> 00:41:33,289
perhaps one day,

691
00:41:35,599 --> 00:41:38,400
I would probably go to my grave...

692
00:41:38,840 --> 00:41:40,000
without knowing...

693
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:45,000
how wrong I was.